[Name] KPowersave
[Summary] An utility used to set power consumption and conservation options.
[Description] KPowersave, the KDE front-end to powersave, can be used to control \
power management and monitor your laptop battery's strength. For example, you can \
configure the screen on your laptop to turn off if the computer is not used for a \
specified amount of time, extending battery life.
